Second Department,

March, 2008

(March 4, 2008) Crystal Agnew, Respondent, v Corner Stone Baptist Church, Appellant, et al., Defendant. [851 NYS2d 893]

There are issues of fact requiring the denial of summary judgment (see CPLR 3212; Alvarez v Prospect Hosp., 68 NY2d 320 [1986]). Rivera, J.P., Miller, Dillon and Belen, JJ., concur.
